longBusinessSummary: T-Flex Techvest PCB Co., Ltd. engages in the manufacture and sale of FPC and PCB products worldwide. The company provides original equipment manufacturing services for printed circuit boards (PCBs) inner layer and outer layer lamination; and PCB inner layer automatic optical inspection. Its products are used in portable devices, camera module, auto CCD, keypad, cell phone hing main boards; LCM module, mobile phone, communication, mother, TFT-LCD, and high-density interconnection boards; and computer peripheral and consumer products, which include notebook and digital camera module. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Taoyuan, Taiwan.
